Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子 到底還是沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨他去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夥計們 回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回Luna
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我默默地注視著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有主人的香榭麗捨三十號
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿如建造在岸邊的砂堡一般
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分崩離析的街市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜靜展開的青空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日的暴風雨已退去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們的夏日一同終結
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終幕\N岸邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}5年後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Je veux vivre au bord de la mer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我願住在海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Pas n'importe quelle mer mais cette mer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了這片海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Et si tu me quittais demain Je serais toujours là
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若明天你離去 我仍在那等待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Et quand le déluge il viendra
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當風暴來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:04:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Peut-être tu ne seras pu là
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:04:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你或已不在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Là où l'amour existait quand nous étions si jeunes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而愛將永存 在青春彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是秘書長閣下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副主編大人親自前來 可真振奮人心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心你玩忽職守啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何了 和平條約的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於面臨締結…了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下我國與帝國的邦交正常化終於成為現實了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫長的戰爭也終於要結束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民間交流日益廣泛 國民團結互助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正繁榮的國度即將誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:05:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而非僅少數人富裕的國家 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不知時勢何時會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此我還是願意相信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信在此時選擇了這個答案的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是見風使舵罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 關於這發言的真意來日再敘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是和等候多時的舊友重逢之日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會忘了預約吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 替我告訴秘書白天的內閣會議會遲到一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼重要的預約 不能拜託秘書去辦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚要在新娛樂城舉杯慶祝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得今天特地來給你看這報導
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「歐仁妮小姐 凱旋公演」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}馬賽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱麗 朱麗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您回來了 馬克西米利安叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別叫我叔叔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事…太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們有乖乖聽埃馬紐埃爾的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 乖乖聽話的人就有禮物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是叔叔 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克西米利安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克西米利安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您理想中的 帝國與地球的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於有結果了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我於本日退役了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後 地球與帝國之間的物資往來將愈加繁盛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我打算買回父親的法老王號
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫埃馬紐埃爾他們做生意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克西米利安先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 馬克西米利安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不趕快出門就趕不上聚會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}約阿尼納
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 您真有眼光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是舶來品 地球貨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴黎名牌產品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟黑髮合襯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 地球的模特小姐真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是配黑髮天衣無縫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝…波
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 不買了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 客人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西怎能配我家公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「您也一定會獲得新生」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 阿里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您也來一杯吧 貝爾圖喬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我正在警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有東西想給您看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏寫著加冕儀式之日 阿爾貝先生將蒞臨此地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且是以地球大使秘書輔佐官的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.10,0:10:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝爾圖喬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若這不能稱之為命運 那還能稱之為何物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是那位大人的指引吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.30,0:10:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您出色完成使命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我將永保和平
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守衛這約阿尼納的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這心意不會動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.10,0:10:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也將追隨您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.50,0:11:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 貝爾圖喬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連通公司航班10272 伽利略至巴黎宇宙空港
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Galileo：木星四顆大型衛星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將進入地球圈外軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵達巴黎時刻將有略微晚點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs22}預計於當地時間2：13抵達…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主犯兩人 貝尼代托和加斯帕爾·卡德魯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全宇宙通緝其下落
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴黎是…兩點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來來 這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會面已結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時光如箭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽您的演奏 這也是第五次了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 今年見面了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那位先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 請自便
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝 神甫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了 弗朗茲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如之前與您聯絡所說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直沒找到買主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 需以物抵過去五年間的稅款
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這塊土地、建築的所有權利將由國家接管
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 沒有異議
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 請在這裏簽名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:14:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 能讓我最後進宅邸一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 現在請自便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿爾貝·埃雷拉」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Herrera：原著中梅爾塞苔絲父親的姓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「費爾南·蒙代戈」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「愛德蒙·唐泰斯」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗茲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這五年間一直很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙耳不聞窗外事 一心只讀聖賢書
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到發現時 就已經二十歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…只是太拚命了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要代替你、父親還有伯爵活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗茲 我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕陷入過去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕就那樣被過去所俘獲 去恨人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 弗朗茲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…一直沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅爾塞苔絲·埃爾達小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多日不見 近來可好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛船終於抵達地球軌道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.00,0:17:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但途中船長一病不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我想無甚大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看來難免有誤歸程
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話 我真想現在就回到您身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏上旅程那天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從機窗看到遠去的馬賽那天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.10,0:18:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那溫暖的陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最珍重之人的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從未有一日不掛念在心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天指引著我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使我無所迷惘 無所困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們光輝燦爛的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請勿掛心 等我歸來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻未能擁您在懷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謹以此言封緘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.40,0:18:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「等待 然後期待」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給親愛的梅爾塞苔絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:19:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真誠的愛德蒙·唐泰斯 敬上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您…早在我出生很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一直在這裏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.30,0:19:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你、和父親、和伯爵度過的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向你發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論走上何種人生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都絕不會忘記那個夏天 絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:24.40,ed3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Harsh words were said\NAnd Lies were told instead
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:24.40,ed4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經快語傷人 也曾謊言欺騙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:30.00,ed3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't ever mean to make you cry
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:30.00,ed4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我無心讓你哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:34.20,ed3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But love can make us weak\Nand can make us strong
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:34.20,ed4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛能使人軟弱 更能使人堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:36.90,ed3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And before to very long
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:36.90,ed4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺之間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:43.50,ed3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was totally in love with you\NI bathed in you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:43.50,ed4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已深深愛上你 為你沉溺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:48.80,ed3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lost in you Captivated by you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:48.80,ed4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為你癡迷 為你魅惑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:54.20,ed3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amazed by you Dazed by you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:54.20,ed4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為你驚異 為你茫然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:58.00,ed3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing can go wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:58.00,ed4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切隨心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.60,0:21:03.20,ed3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing can go wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.60,0:21:03.20,ed4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切如意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:11.20,ed3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So tonight I'll sing a song to all my friends
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:11.20,ed4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜讓我為所有朋友歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:16.40,ed3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also to those we won't be seeing again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:16.40,ed4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為無法再見的友人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.60,0:21:20.80,ed3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To those I knew And those I still adore
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.60,0:21:20.80,ed4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為我的舊識 為我的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:23.50,ed3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I want to see once more
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:23.50,ed4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為想再見的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:28.00,ed3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just pray that you will love me and
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:28.00,ed4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只願你能愛我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:30.10,ed3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:30.10,ed4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信任我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.40,0:21:35.20,ed3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Laugh with me and cry with me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.40,0:21:35.20,ed4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共同歡笑 共同流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:40.30,ed3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spend those silent time with me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:40.30,ed4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共同度過平靜每日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:44.90,ed3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love me evermore
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:44.90,ed4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠愛我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:49.50,ed3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love me evermore
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:49.50,ed4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠愛我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.80,0:21:55.80,ed3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You and I were lovers
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.80,0:21:55.80,ed4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們曾是戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.90,0:21:59.90,ed3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our dreams were not soured by life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.90,0:21:59.90,ed4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想不曾被人生毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:05.40,ed3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then my friends' betrayal
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:05.40,ed4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而朋友的背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.50,0:22:12.70,ed3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meant you never will be my wife
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.50,0:22:12.70,ed4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們無法在一起
